This directory contains 3 files:

input-OPAL.in		==> Input file for OPAL simulation of the perfect diode with thermal emittance

run-opal.py		==> Python script for launching simulations. This script will need to be edited
			    in order to specify the directory path where the simulation will be run etc.

subroutines.py		==> Contains Python functions used by run-opal.py
